text: Sambia is a peninsula in Prussia (Russian Kaliningrad Oblast). Sambia may also refer to: *Sambia, Comoros, a town on the island of Mohéli in the Comoros *Sambia (Papua New Guinea), a tribe of people in the Eastern Highlands Province of Papua New Guinea ==See also== *Sambians, an extinct Old Prussian tribe *Zambia, a country in Africa
title: Sambia (disambiguation)
